test_large_range:
assert [] == [2, 3, 4]
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: 2
  Full diff:
  - [2, 3, 4]
  + []
test_even_range:
assert [1, 3] == [4, 6, 8]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 4
  Right contains one more item: 8
  Full diff:
  - [4, 6, 8]
  + [1, 3]
test_zero_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4] == []
  Left contains 4 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [1, 2, 3, 4]
